fields.name: MaxDegreeOfParallelismPerJob
fields.description: The maximum degree of parallelism per job this user can use to submit jobs. This property, the min priority per job property, or both must be passed.

fields.name: MinPriorityPerJob
fields.description: The minimum priority per job this user can use to submit jobs. This property, the max degree of parallelism per job property, or both must be passed.

fields.name: ObjectId
fields.description: The AAD object identifier for the entity to create a policy for.

fields.name: ObjectType
fields.description: The type of AAD object the object identifier refers to.
